import React from 'react'
import "./index.css"
import Home from "./routes/Home"
import Pokemon from "./routes/Pokemon"
import {Route, Routes} from "react-router-dom"

const App = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <Routes>
      <Route path = "/" element = {<Home/>} />
      <Route path = "/" element = {<Pokemon/>} />
    </Routes>
    </>
  )
}

export default App
